snippet.title: BRIXITY Pre-Registration Trailer 🌱
snippet.description:
RESTORE. RECRUIT. REBUILD!

BRIXITY is coming to iOS and Google play on August 24th 🧱🌎 Get ready to build your world, Brix-by-Brix!

Pre-register for BRIXITY now to unlock all kinds of exclusive rewards at launch! Be sure to also sign up for Early Access while you're at it!

Pre-register and apply for Early Access here 👉 https://go.playbrixity.com/preregister

#BRIXITY #PlayBRIXITY #BrixByBrix #Preregistration
